data.description: Split foyer 5 BR/3BA home in sought after Jefferson City School district. Upper/Main level features a spacious living room, formal dining room, and kitchen open to living room. Main floor also features large primary suite with tray ceilings and a large bath with double vanity, huge walk-in closet, soaking tub and separate shower. Two secondary bedrooms on the main level share a full bath. Additional flex space on lower level includes kitchenette area with wash basin and refrigerator and a large room that could be used as family room, entertaining area, game room, or other endless possibilities. Two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom are located on the lower level as well.     **NEW** back deck and privacy fence facing the road!  Note that entire back yard is fenced.  Majority of fencing is upgraded vinyl coated chain link, but there is a privacy fence facing the road frontage for aesthetics.  Privacy fence has a drive in gate on one side of the home and a walk through gate on the other side of the home for your convenience.    Additional covered arbor at the front of the home has hooks for a porch swing so you can enjoy the peaceful outdoors.    Home boasts convenient access to I-85, less than 30 minutes to Athens and only 15 minutes to outlet shopping in Commerce.
